          <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300">
            <p class="mb-4">
              The internet was designed as a passive network for moving data between clients and servers. Today's AI is bolted onto this outdated architecture, leading to centralized control, privacy violations, and limited intelligence capabilities. Acratos reimagines the internet from the ground up with intelligence as a native layer. 
              The time for half-measures is over. The future is decentralized, and it's not just an option‚Äîit's a necessity.
            </p>
