                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-semibold">No more surveillance capitalism</span> selling your attention to the highest bidder</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white">
              The revolution won't be centralized. Will you build it with us?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

      <!-- Problems & Solutions -->
      <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
